p: Major resistant mutations were present in very low frequency in the transmission cluster. Major Protease Inhibitors (PIs) resistance mutations were present in only one patient (V82F); major Nucleoside and Non-Nucleoside Reverse-transcriptase Inhibitors (NRTIs, NNRTIs) resistance mutations were present in only another patient (NRTI: M184V + K219E; NNRTI: K103N).
